  "description": "<p>Portfolio: BusinessPartner <br /></p><p><strong>Job Scope: </strong></p><p>•\tPartner business units in managing the end-to-end employee lifecycle</p><p>•\tProvide first-line advisory support on HR and people-related matters</p><p>•\tSupport manpower planning and resourcing strategies to meet departmental needs</p><p>•\tPartner Heads of Departments on talent acquisition, engagement, and retention initiatives</p><p>•\tReview and improve HR processes to enhance efficiency and effectiveness</p><p>•\tParticipate in HR projects and initiatives as required</p><p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Min. Bachelor’s degree, preferably in Human Resource, Business Administration, or a related field</li><li>Min. 3-4  years’ relevant experience in HR business partnering etc </li><li>Experience as an HR Generalist in a healthcare setting/ Non profit organization is an advantage</li></ul><p>For interested applicants, please send your updated resume to: melissa@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p>All candidates’ information will be treated with the strictest confidence</p><p>Melissa Zhang Zhiqi (Mezzo)</p><p>R2197564</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd</p><p>99C4599</p>",
